### Generate Recipes
POST http://localhost:3001/ai/recipes/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "ingredients": ["eggs", "tomatoes", "cheese", "bread", "milk", "butter"],
    "allergies": ["peanuts"],
    "dietPreference": "VEGETARIAN",
    "count": 3
}

### Generate Recipes (minimal - just ingredients)
POST http://localhost:3001/ai/recipes/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "ingredients": ["chicken", "rice", "onion", "garlic"]
}

### Ask AI a general question
POST http://localhost:3001/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "query": "What can I make with eggs and cheese for breakfast?",
    "ingredients": ["eggs", "cheese", "milk", "bread", "butter"]
}

### Ask AI about a specific recipe (substitutions)
POST http://localhost:3001/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "query": "How can I make this recipe vegan?",
    "recipe": {
        "title": "Cheese Omelette",
        "ingredients": [
            { "name": "eggs", "amount": "3" },
            { "name": "cheddar cheese", "amount": "50g" },
            { "name": "butter", "amount": "1 tbsp" }
        ],
        "steps": ["Beat eggs", "Melt butter in pan", "Pour eggs", "Add cheese", "Fold and serve"]
    }
}

### Ask AI about a recipe (variations)
POST http://localhost:3001/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "query": "What spices would make this more interesting?",
    "recipe": {
        "title": "Scrambled Eggs",
        "ingredients": [
            { "name": "eggs", "amount": "2" },
            { "name": "salt", "amount": "pinch" }
        ]
    },
    "ingredients": ["paprika", "cumin", "oregano", "chili flakes", "turmeric"]
}

### Ask AI (simple question, no context)
POST http://localhost:3001/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "query": "How do I make a perfect omelette?"
}

